     C     *INZSR        BEGSR

     C     *entry        PLIST
     C                   PARM                    RtnCode
     C                   PARM                    StreamFile
     C                   PARM                    SourceDir
     C                   PARM                    DestDir
     C                   PARM                    Action
     C                   PARM                    Option
     C                   PARM                    User
     C                   PARM                    Password
